The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Coaching camp under lights

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: Now, school kids aspiring to become cricketers will have a taste of playing under lights. 

The Balaka Sangha School of Cricket and former India player Devang Gandhi have joined hands to form a coaching camp. Coaching faculty includes Gopal Bose, Utpal Chatterjee, Mintoo Das and Ajay Verma. The camp will be held on all days except for Wednesday and Friday. 




